{"lemma":"صُرَّةٍ","slug":"صُرَّةٍ","root":"ص.ر.ر","root_slug":"ص-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صُرَّةٍ","root":"صرر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24069","n24070","n24071"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"purse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"package"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare صَرَّ (ṣarra, “to tie up, to pack”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24069","headword_ar":"صَرَّةٌ","root":"Sr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vociferation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clamour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, TA:) so in the Kur li. 29: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most vehement vociferation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clamour"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crying"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, M, K *) of a man and of a bird &c. (Zj, M.) [In the K, this meaning is erroneously assigned to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sir~apN","text_ar":"صِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vehemence"},{"kind":"text","text":"of grief or anxiety (S, M, K) and of war (M, K) and of heat, (K,) or of the hot season, (M,) &c.: (S, M:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence of the heat"},{"kind":"text","text":"of summer. (S, A.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A contraction,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much contraction, and sternness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moroseness, of the face,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of dislike,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hatred."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A company, a collection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assemblage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K.) So in the following words of Imra-el-Keys:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"jawaAHiruhaA fiY Sar~apK lamo tuzay~ali"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Those of them that remained behind, in a herd, not dispersed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(EM p. 48: [see the entire verse voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwnN","text_ar":"دُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY Sr~p","text_ar":"فى صرّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"here means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the midst of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clamour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in vehemence of grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anxiety."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M.)       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaTofapN","text_ar":"عَطْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain bead"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarazapN","text_ar":"خَرَزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which women fascinate men so as to withhold them from other women."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M, K, TA. [This is evidently what is meant by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaTofap","text_ar":"عَطْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", but is given in the M and K as a signification distinct therefrom.])       -A4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSar~aApN","text_ar":"مُصَرَّاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n24070","headword_ar":"صُرَّةٌ","root":"Sr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A purse"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arajN","text_ar":"شَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", M, K, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arojN","text_ar":"شَرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for money;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSar~N","text_ar":"مَصَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, (TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSar~N","text_ar":"مِصَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (so in a copy of the A:) pl. of the first,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SurazN","text_ar":"صُرَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) Hence the prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotaHo Suraraka taEolamo Eujaraka","text_ar":"اِفْتَحْ صُرَرَكَ تَعْلَمْ عُجَرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Return to thyself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lay open the recesses of thy mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thou wilt know"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy vices,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faults,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy good from thy evil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuradN","text_ar":"صُرَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last explanation.])"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n24071","headword_ar":"صِرَّةٌ","root":"Sr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sir~N","text_ar":"صِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}